    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>Write a function <code>int spawn_process()</code> that creates a child process using <code>fork()</code>. The function must:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Return 1 in the <strong>child process</strong></li>
  <li>Return 0 in the <strong>parent process</strong></li>
  <li>Return -1 if <code>fork()</code> fails</li>
</ul>
<p>The test will verify that both the child and parent return correctly. You do not need to print the process ID.</p>]]></text>
